 because St Thomas's doubts have made him seem a very human character."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Thomas de Venator de Boyleston was born about 1090, in England, United Kingdom. She had at least 3 daughters with Thomas de Venator de Boyleston."},"et":{"about 1090–":"umbes 1090–Surnud","1084–Male":"1084–Surnud","1115–1185":"1115–1185","1115–Female":"1115–Surnud","1135–Female":"1135–Surnud","1090–Female":"1090–Surnud","1090":"1090","1115":"1115","about 1090":"umbes 1090","1135":"1135","about 1115":"umbes 1115","1185":"1185","about 1135":"umbes 1135","1084":"1084","Sydenham Damerel, Devon, England":"Sydenham Damerel, Devon, England","Boylestone, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom":"Boylestone, Derbyshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England, United Kingdom":"Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1090–":"noin 1090–Kuollut","1084–Male":"1084–Kuollut","1115–1185":"1115–1185","1115–Female":"1115–Kuollut","1135–Female":"1135–Kuollut","1090–Female":"1090–Kuollut","1090":"1090","1115":"1115","about 1090":"noin 1090","1135":"1135","about 1115":"noin 1115","1185":"1185","about 1135":"noin 1135","1084":"1084","Sydenham Damerel, Devon, England":"Sydenham Damerel, Devon, England","Boylestone, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom":"Boylestone, Derbyshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England, United Kingdom":"Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1090–":"environ 1090–Décédée","1084–Male":"1084–Décédé","1115–1185":"1115–1185","1115–Female":"1115–Décédée","1135–Female":"1135–Décédée","1090–Female":"1090–Décédée","1090":"1090","1115":"1115","about 1090":"environ 1090","1135":"1135","about 1115":"environ 1115","1185":"1185","about 1135":"environ 1135","1084":"1084","Sydenham Damerel, Devon, England":"Sydenham Damerel, Devon, Angleterre","Boylestone, Derbyshire, England, United Kingdom":"Boylestone, Derbyshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","England, United Kingdom":"Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs Thomas de Venator de Boyleston est née environ 10